Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.69,0:02:20.87,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta pee.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:31.14,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,"Maintenance confirmation of connection line to Headquarters...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.14,0:02:35.63,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,...for the purpose of high-level emergency situations, Mission"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:38.01,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What an amazing name.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:40.31,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite an important mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.31,0:02:44.03,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Failure will result in disciplinary action for the whole platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.59,0:02:48.95,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,There are certain conditions under which a level-one alert will be announced,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.95,0:02:52.79,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,and all the surrounding forces will be put into an emergency standby as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.16,0:02:57.23,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, it's truly something of great importance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.17,0:03:00.94,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What kind of mission is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.64,0:03:02.66,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.38,0:03:06.54,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Watching the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.69,0:03:08.62,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.32,0:03:14.94,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So you know that this phone is a hotline connected to the government center, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:17.32,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times has it rung before?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:18.25,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Not once.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.25,0:03:20.68,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, thankfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:22.05,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:24.40,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It's a problem if it rings,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.40,0:03:27.72,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,but it'll be even more of a problem if it doesn't ring when it should.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:32.60,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why they need to confirm that the line is working twice a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:33.39,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is the...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.39,0:03:36.02,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,"Maintenance... um..."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.02,0:03:38.46,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, remember it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.46,0:03:41.14,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,"Maintenance of the connection line..."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.14,0:03:41.83,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:43.00,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:45.41,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,"Maintenance confirmation to Headquarters..."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:50.51,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,"Maintenance confirmation of the connection line to Headquarters...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.51,0:03:53.66,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,...for the purpose of high-level emergency situations, Mission"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:55.04,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:59.71,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Me! Me, me, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:02.26,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me carry out that mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:05.23,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to try talking on a phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.23,0:04:07.35,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that something to be exited about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.77,0:04:11.82,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Its basic functions are similar to the Takemikazuchi's intercom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.82,0:04:13.73,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The only difference is the distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.73,0:04:15.46,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:18.86,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so wonderful to be able to speak with someone who's far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.46,0:04:25.01,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess you could say it {\i1}does{\i0} feel a bit weird talking to someone you can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.67,0:04:28.07,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But, it's nothing special once you're used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:32.72,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The problem is, we don't know exactly when it will ring today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:34.08,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still want to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.45,0:04:35.45,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:40.51,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright then, you're going to stick to the phone for the whole day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.87,0:04:46.35,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring-ring-ring....
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.23,0:04:50.71,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Helvetian Republic Army 1121st Platoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:53.04,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Private Kanata speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.97,0:05:00.29,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,And after the call is finished, put this back on the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.29,0:05:01.21,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:43.93,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Fi-Fili{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.93,0:05:46.35,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,My, you're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.53,0:05:49.08,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:52.20,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? Jeez, I can't stand watching this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.46,0:05:54.29,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna miss the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:55.33,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Train?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.01,0:05:59.70,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a document I need to deliver to Headquarters as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:02.36,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Claus-san is coming next week, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.97,0:06:04.38,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going to the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.19,0:06:07.44,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you to watch the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.44,0:06:08.06,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:14.18,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,If it rings and you're not there, the worst possible outcome is that they'll think we're under attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:15.48,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So take it seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:17.49,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:40.71,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:42.23,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.23,0:06:43.30,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't sleeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.30,0:06:45.22,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't sleeping at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:48.09,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.09,0:06:49.59,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She wasn't in her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:51.75,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.19,0:06:53.75,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's in the hangar again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.55,0:06:55.64,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:58.76,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Kanata, what do you want for lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.76,0:07:00.35,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I-I'll cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.03,0:07:03.49,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. It's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.49,0:07:04.23,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:11.12,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why do both you and Kureha never let me do the cooking when it's my turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:15.49,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I cooked quite a bit before the both of you came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:17.67,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.67,0:07:19.45,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure it doesn't taste bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.45,0:07:23.70,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's true, it doesn't taste as bad as it looks...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.45,0:07:25.26,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.26,0:07:28.06,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I-it has a unique flavor, it's lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.46,0:07:29.84,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:34.31,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright then, today I'll push my skills to the absolute limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.80,0:07:37.81,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, anybody home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:39.50,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.50,0:07:41.79,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, it's Naomi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:45.31,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.66,0:07:49.49,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't go far from the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:51.69,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You've got a guest!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.79,0:07:54.92,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, alright then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:57.54,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a sec! I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.03,0:08:05.70,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna eat another sandwich full of cutting board chips.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.44,0:08:10.42,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,These are...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:12.95,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You can drink them. It's apple cider.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:16.89,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,These were made on the hill where we buy our apple juice from.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:21.93,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means they're related to our Calvados, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.09,0:08:27.44,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so you knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:35.56,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Two should be enough as a gift, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.33,0:08:38.18,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:39.20,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Gift?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.15,0:08:43.14,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,They're holding a merchant's guild meeting in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.14,0:08:47.81,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,They help us with accommodations, so we occasionally give them gifts in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.81,0:08:48.96,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:49.87,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:54.93,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What a letdown. Those girls were trying so hard to hide it from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.94,0:08:58.50,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.07,0:09:02.57,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:05.48,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you when the time is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.18,0:09:10.72,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, how about having lunch with us, Naomi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.09,0:09:12.86,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:15.00,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to attend, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:17.85,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You remember the news in this week's paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.85,0:09:21.65,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems everyone wants some kind of explanation from the Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.65,0:09:22.62,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,News?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:26.21,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,About the treaty conference going through trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:27.85,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.31,0:09:32.84,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,They still haven't reached an agreement about reparations and borders.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:35.28,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not uncommon for it to drag on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.95,0:09:41.02,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I really think those gramps from the guild just wanted to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:45.10,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you played the role of the Fire Maiden in the Water Festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:47.42,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,it seems your fanbase has grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:49.79,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a bit troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.79,0:09:50.87,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:56.28,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So that being said, it seems that I need to head out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:09:59.96,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also a maiden of the fortress in both mind and body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.96,0:10:02.03,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I can complete the mission on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.26,0:10:05.03,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.03,0:10:05.63,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.78,0:10:12.42,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, I'm giving this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.57,0:10:16.05,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my old stuff, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:19.20,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a trumpet book!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.36,0:10:23.05,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This is wonderful, so wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:24.75,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.75,0:10:28.03,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotten better at the trumpet, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.03,0:10:30.06,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a reward for your efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:33.90,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, it'll probably help you stay up during the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.82,0:10:41.80,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.39,0:10:43.91,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This is C.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.53,0:10:45.77,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,D.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.77,0:10:48.92,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,E, F, G.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:51.36,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,A.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:09.76,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer's almost over, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.35,0:11:20.40,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Iliya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.00,0:11:26.56,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I drank too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.60,0:11:36.70,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Noel-chan, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.70,0:11:39.59,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's raining! The laundry is getting drenched!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.04,0:11:45.28,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The courtyard is within the mission parameters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:54.39,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka...na...ta!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.39,0:11:56.02,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:11:58.57,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.57,0:12:00.58,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka...na...ta!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.58,0:12:01.95,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:03.94,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.95,0:12:16.96,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:20.21,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}Don't mention it. It's good the laundry is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.21,0:12:21.88,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}I really appreciate{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:26.68,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}No wait, I-I'm so sorry for making you help me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:28.26,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:32.02,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}We also apologize for showing up without prior notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.02,0:12:36.80,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to give my regards since I'm returning to Treize tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:39.13,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.13,0:12:41.56,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to give your regards to a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:45.31,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true at all, Seiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:49.49,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I was told that he's been quite rude to the people of this base,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.82,0:12:53.66,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought we should come by to apologize, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.55,0:12:55.66,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.66,0:12:57.73,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,They all went out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.73,0:13:01.26,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The one with black hair, Rio-san if I'm not mistaken, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:02.17,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.70,0:13:04.29,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.29,0:13:05.64,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping to see her{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:09.18,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this book yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:10.63,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.63,0:13:12.22,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,A trumpet book.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:14.26,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio-senpai gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.65,0:13:15.94,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:17.65,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,As I expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.51,0:13:21.06,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no. Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.06,0:13:23.07,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just talking to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:25.13,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So are you by yourself right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:27.20,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I am. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:32.08,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the middle of the "Maintenance confirmation of connection line to Headquarters...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:36.23,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,for the purpose of high-level emergency situations, Mission".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.74,0:13:37.42,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.42,0:13:41.42,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So I would assume,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.07,0:13:44.60,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,you're waiting for this to ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.60,0:13:45.18,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:50.20,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is the first time I'm using it, so I'm a bit nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:53.97,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I can properly handle the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.42,0:13:56.44,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we practice, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.05,0:14:04.69,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So Yumina-san is also attending the guild meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:09.92,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she's raising donations from the people of the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.92,0:14:11.76,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, have a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.19,0:14:16.51,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.51,0:14:17.65,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.65,0:14:18.96,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Have some too, Seiya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.64,0:14:21.09,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll drink it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.09,0:14:23.66,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,but this doesn't make us friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:31.72,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you making?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:35.47,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you both recognize this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:36.97,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.97,0:14:47.65,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really a phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:49.42,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's a phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.89,0:14:54.32,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The kids love it, so I make it for them sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.32,0:14:55.61,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Seiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.61,0:14:56.66,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:59.28,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,A phone, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.58,0:15:04.52,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:06.77,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.77,0:15:08.78,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! It's awesome, Seiya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.78,0:15:10.68,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.68,0:15:14.78,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you should first say, "hello" on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:17.38,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:19.36,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.59,0:15:24.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This is great! I really heard a voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.53,0:15:27.27,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You can use it for practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:27.73,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.06,0:15:30.73,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.73,0:15:32.23,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.23,0:15:33.74,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:37.75,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Helvetian Republic Army 1121st Platoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.75,0:15:40.31,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Private Sorami Kanata speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.31,0:15:41.75,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.58,0:15:45.75,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm honored to receive your call today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:47.94,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.94,0:15:50.05,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,And... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.71,0:15:52.05,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, birdy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:54.01,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.01,0:15:55.00,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.00,0:15:56.04,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:00.32,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.02,0:16:14.99,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:37.47,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Is the priest and the{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.48,0:16:59.45,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.46,0:17:04.71,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my dear God...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.27,0:17:06.96,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:10.50,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You were supposed to come here to apologize,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.12,0:17:13.81,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,but you just played around and caused trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:16.83,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,No dinner for you tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.83,0:17:18.17,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.17,0:17:19.63,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:27.68,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay now, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.68,0:17:30.25,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But your clothes are wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.25,0:17:32.36,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay, I have an extra{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.34,0:17:38.87,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.78,0:17:44.87,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:47.10,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,is so embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:49.15,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,No it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.15,0:17:51.79,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're so dazzling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.06,0:17:56.43,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But, thanks, Yumina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.43,0:17:58.56,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wash these and return it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.56,0:18:00.30,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, you can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.13,0:18:03.25,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too big for the kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:08.16,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,and I can't find anyone more suitable for it than you, Kanata-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:12.93,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.52,0:18:15.14,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I come and play again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.14,0:18:16.00,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.00,0:18:17.88,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You can come again too, Seiya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.88,0:18:19.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.67,0:18:29.21,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll come if I don't have anything else to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:31.99,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, we will excuse ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.99,0:18:35.21,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,May you be blessed with great happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.95,0:18:38.85,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.65,0:18:45.65,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, time to clean this up...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.88,0:18:48.10,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I almost forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.10,0:18:49.31,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.77,0:19:26.08,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta pee.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.84,0:20:18.83,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone, come back soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.83,0:20:21.50,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.19,0:20:29.26,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, those geezers...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.26,0:20:30.75,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kana{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:32.44,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.97,0:20:36.46,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg of you, help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:38.96,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened, Kanata?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.49,0:20:41.47,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I... Can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:45.51,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna wet myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:48.12,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Go already, you'll get sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.12,0:20:50.39,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.99,0:20:53.85,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been holding it the whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.85,0:20:56.81,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Either she's too devoted, or overly honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.18,0:21:05.32,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.98,0:21:08.06,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:10.57,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.24,0:21:12.70,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I... Can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.70,0:21:14.93,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take another step!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.62,0:21:18.08,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She has amazingly bad timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.10,0:21:24.86,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, this is Helvetian Republic Army 1121st Platoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.86,0:21:26.57,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant Rio Kazumiya speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.65,0:21:29.59,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.26,0:21:33.64,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard we need to confirm the line to your post,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.64,0:21:34.66,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,so I insisted{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.26,0:21:36.10,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you running away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.41,0:21:38.63,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.75,0:21:43.34,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you haven't forgiven me yet, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.64,0:21:47.11,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.87,0:21:49.00,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.00,0:21:52.12,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Please save this country, save Helvetia!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.17,0:21:56.63,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.07,0:21:58.48,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Noel-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.48,0:22:01.38,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... Since this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.96,0:22:04.63,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I sleep well in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.63,0:22:06.26,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.32,0:22:11.47,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ba{\fscx300}-{\fscx100} My!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.01,0:22:15.01,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What a cute dress you're wearing, Kana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.01,0:22:18.15,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, what are you two doing in the hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.53,0:22:20.09,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata fell down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.09,0:22:20.99,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She can't stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.99,0:22:22.02,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.02,0:22:23.15,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.15,0:22:25.41,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Then stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.71,0:22:31.70,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, you're so hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.70,0:22:32.88,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What a spoiled girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.88,0:22:35.01,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.64,0:22:37.96,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready, set...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.96,0:22:41.17,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nooooo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.62,0:24:19.93,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Next episode: A Typhoon Passes - Illusion And Reality.
